Prophetess Mary Omolara Alarape of the Christ Mount Zion Bethel Healing Ministry, s Lagos-Ibadan Expressway, Ogun State, has advised Christians to be exemplary in showing genuine love. Alarape gave the counsel during a maiden charity sales initiative tagged ‘Jesus Market’ as part of the activities to demonstrate love and care as well create a welfare package for members of the church and people at large. The initiative held through her late husband’s foundation, Pastor Samuel Alarape Foundation, in conjunction with the Christ Mount Zion Bethel Healing Ministry, benefitted about 500 persons who bought food items, clothes and other household items at largely discounted price.